    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135650/extras/8718e9bcdf36e9c879cfeff30f08e161.poster.avif?t=1746912575\" width=616 height=229 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135650/extras/8718e9bcdf36e9c879cfeff30f08e161.webm?t=1746912575\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>A NEW CHALLENGE</strong></h2> After an act of desperation and courage, Ayo finds himself separated from his mother and adrift in the ocean. Upon finding solid ground, he encounters a new and challenging land—a place full of mysteries and dangers. Face a variety of enemies, from wild animals to hostile indigenous warriors, as you explore dense forests, open fields, and dark caves.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135650/extras/913f337d6fb2a823dcbc0f5101f2821d.poster.avif?t=1746912575\" width=616 height=262 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135650/extras/913f337d6fb2a823dcbc0f5101f2821d.webm?t=1746912575\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135650/extras/913f337d6fb2a823dcbc0f5101f2821d.mp4?t=1746912575\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>FEATURES</strong></h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> A pixelated game made especially for genre lovers, an experience bordering on nostalgia;<br></li><li> Explore the Southern Map with its beautiful fauna and flora;<br></li><li> Help the character face unique enemies as you progress, collect items and resources;<br></li><li> Fight with native weapons: axe, spear, blowgun, and bow and arrow;<br></li><li> Meet the bosses, unique entities, and battles in 2D platform style;<br></li><li> Mini-games, side quests, and engaging stories.</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135650/extras/058da58179330290e18ca04ff02e7b83.poster.avif?t=1746912575\" width=616 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135650/extras/058da58179330290e18ca04ff02e7b83.webm?t=1746912575\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135650/extras/058da58179330290e18ca04ff02e7b83.mp4?t=1746912575\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135650/extras/4165c2a88c112d3aa253d475f3e1fd95.apng?t=1746912575\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135650/extras/4165c2a88c112d3aa253d475f3e1fd95.poster.avif?t=1746912575\" class=\"bb_img\" width=616 height=229 /></picture></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>BRAVE HERO</strong></h2> In this Demo, help Ayo explore 14 maps, encountering various challenges and receiving tips from native NPCs to find and rescue her mother. Face enemies, increase your XP, collect resources, buy items from shops, and confront 3 unique Entity Bosses.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135650/extras/14fecb22327ab4e39e04bf4bb756701e.poster.avif?t=1746912575\" width=632 height=424 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135650/extras/14fecb22327ab4e39e04bf4bb756701e.webm?t=1746912575\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135650/extras/14fecb22327ab4e39e04bf4bb756701e.mp4?t=1746912575\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>ÓGA MAP</strong></h2> Find Ayo's Refuge House, created as a sanctuary for the player to rest, fish, collect new resources, craft exclusive foods, and unique handcrafted items.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135650/extras/9c98e1837ab2c390102b36fc32037b9e.poster.avif?t=1746912575\" width=758 height=354 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135650/extras/9c98e1837ab2c390102b36fc32037b9e.webm?t=1746912575\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135650/extras/9c98e1837ab2c390102b36fc32037b9e.mp4?t=1746912575\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135650/extras/d49c32c6cb88c069ea58f494809d9fe2.apng?t=1746912575\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135650/extras/d49c32c6cb88c069ea58f494809d9fe2.poster.avif?t=1746912575\" class=\"bb_img\" width=616 height=229 /></picture></span>",
